            "title": "標普維持預測今明年樓價無升跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"標普維持預測今明年樓價無升跌\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3VzPu6AiAo5iYwcfDEYhQA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/39c02570-94e9-11f0-a87f-c67f7d75d6aa\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">標普維持預測今明年樓價無升跌</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
